	<h2>What are campaigns?</h2>
	<div class="box-content">
		<p>To collect multiple insights, group can launch a campaign and summarize individual user’s insights into one united theme.</p>
		<p>Basically campaign is group’s organized and coordinated effort to promote content production to a specified theme.</p>
		<p>Adding content to campaign requires group membership. To join, go to group’s homepage.</p>
		<p>Moreover, users can only link their own already published contents to a campaign. One content can be linked to multiple campaigns.</p>
		<p>Group admin can also link own campaigns to other campaigns, which help similar campaigns to join forces.</p>
	</div>
